This file lists planned features for future versions of netstatAX25.

Completed Tasks (Version 1.0.1)

    Display Va: Added the display of the Va value (Unacknowledged Frames)
    to the output, integrated with full compatibility.

    Documentation: Updated the README.md and CHANGELOG to reflect the new Va feature.

Next Planned Version (v1.1.0)

    Code Cleanup: Review error handling functions to ensure messages remain
    consistent after the addition of Va functionality.
    (This task remains as a final quality check).
